### Gmail / Google Workspace SMTP (server-side only; configure in Vercel)
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your_email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=your_google_app_password

### Contact routing
CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=your_inbox@example.com

# Optional: override From header (defaults to SMTP_USER)
# CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL=your_email@gmail.com

